{"tid":1792492,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人要反古，唔止反中反共","createTime":"2019-12-21T16:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T15:43:43.000Z","uid":149978,"like":6,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be33c59dfa0d8986cd3d75ffc75d05a096dca8a7","tid":1792492,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:36:32.000Z","msg":"中共的專制極權，其實係繼承古代極權政體的遺留物<br />\n<br />\n古代政權，殺學者，殺異己，亂殺人，多不勝數<br />\n<br />\n例證：<br />\n湯若望來華，改革中國曆法，引入科學，結果被收監，他的朋友就被處死。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲曾發起獵巫行動。把女人的胎記當成魔鬼印記，然後殺這些女巫。<br />\n<br />\n天主教曾搞異端裁判所，把異見人士監禁及處死。<br />\n<br />\n今日中共控制言論，封殺異見人士，其實都係古代遺物。<br />\n<br />\n西方已經進步，脫離獨裁專制與迷信，有普選有公投<br />\n<br />\n中共停滯不前，拒絕進步，雖有現代科技，但政治社會，仍停留在封建時代，繼續擁抱獨裁專制"},{"pid":"6a888c34a1b3b798710a363f64ebdecf1a35f1c8","tid":1792492,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"香港人要反古舊時想，反封建"},{"pid":"16d509c80105ebfcf5e043fac1c5215ad742fcec","tid":1792492,"uid":261773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"文革破四舊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fadfcdae1f6882fd94f739ec9aeb99c8535076e","tid":1792492,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"天主教依家存在"},{"pid":"cf5372b2c2d7ec1d58bb64b24f896ee2c150bc9a","tid":1792492,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"16d509c80105ebfcf5e043fac1c5215ad742fcec","tid":1792492,"uid":261773,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"文革破四舊？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T17:31:27.000Z","msg":"有文明人唔做走去做中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f791d0312c761c922f672fa3dfce6f4d7a4d4667","tid":1792492,"uid":224479,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"16d509c80105ebfcf5e043fac1c5215ad742fcec","tid":1792492,"uid":261773,"l